than you think<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The train from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/kandy-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Kandy<\/a> to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/ella-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ella<\/a> should take around 6 hours. However, everything runs a little slower in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Sri Lanka<\/a>, and there can be longer stops and delays on the journey. In reality, it can take up to 10 hours, but that means more time to see the beautiful views! It might be a long ride, but it&#x2019;s 100% worth the journey.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222311\/sri-lanka-nine-arch-bridge-03.jpg\" alt=\"sri lanka train travel kandy ella\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"sri lanka train travel kandy ella\" class=\"wp-image-73795 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222311\/sri-lanka-nine-arch-bridge-03.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222311\/sri-lanka-nine-arch-bridge-03-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222311\/sri-lanka-nine-arch-bridge-03-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222311\/sri-lanka-nine-arch-bridge-03-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222311\/sri-lanka-nine-arch-bridge-03-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222311\/sri-lanka-nine-arch-bridge-03-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/1