 target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Kandy<\/a> to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/ella-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ella<\/a>, which is why it&#x2019;s so popular.<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2605&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18232822\/train-sri-lanka-kandy-ella-3.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18232822\/train-sri-lanka-kandy-ella-3-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18232822\/train-sri-lanka-kandy-ella-3-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Kandy to Ella Train: An Unforgettable Experience in Sri Lanka\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>3. Take the morning train<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Taking the morning train from <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/kandy-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Kandy<\/a> to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/ella-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ella<\/a> is the best idea, as you&#x2019;ll get daylight throughout your trip and be able to enjoy the epic views as you hang out the doors. After all, you don&#x2019;t want to end up traveling at night and miss them altogether. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/train-kandy-ella\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Get Kandy Train Tickets here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p>If you can, we also recommend avoiding weekends &#x2013; this is the busiest time, and it can be tough to get a seat. Standing for 9 hours is not fun!<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222405\/train-sri-lanka-4.jpg\" alt=\"train station sri lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"train station sri lanka\" class=\"wp-image-73803 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222405\/train-sri-lanka-4.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222405\/train-sri-lanka-4-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/