text-format-boundary=\"true\">Get Kandy Train Tickets here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7.jpg\" alt=\"blue train sri lanka kandy ella\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"blue train sri lanka kandy ella\" class=\"wp-image-73809 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222447\/train-sri-lanka-7.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>6. Bring food with you<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The train itself doesn&#x2019;t have anywhere you can buy food. However, the best thing about the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/kandy-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Kandy<\/a> to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/ella-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ella<\/a> train ride is the local vendors who jump on at each station to sell their goods. You&#x2019;ll hear them shouting and singing their prices as they walk between the cabins with steaming baskets off spicy fried snacks, salty peanuts, or fresh fruit. Make sure to have a little bit of cash on you so that you can indulge.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/how-to-plan-trip\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How to plan a trip!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>7. Check out Kandy train station<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The train ride might be beautiful, but so is <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/kandy-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Kandy<\/a> train station! Look up and see the traditional white iron shelter and the gold station signs. As the old-fashioned train pulls into the station &#x2013; and people wave out the train &#x2013; you could feel as if you stepped back in time.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-1080x720.jpg\" alt=\"kandy trainstation\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"kandy trainstation\" class=\"wp-image-73805 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-1440x960.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222417\/train-sri-lanka-5-1080x720.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-train-classes\">Train Classes<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Typically, first-class tickets are the best option on any train. However, the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/kandy-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Kandy<\/a> to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/sri-lanka\/ella-sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ella<\/a> train is the opposite! The first-class cabin is airconditioned, so you can&#x2019;t open the windows or doors to take photos. It also means no cool breeze from the tea plantations as you zoom through the valley. This is a big part of the experience, so we recommend choosing second or third class instead.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In the second class, you&#x2019;ll have a fan to help with the heat, and you&#x2019;ll also be able to dangle your feet out the door, which is such a buzz and gives you the most incredible views! The third class is a little more uncomfortable, but you&#x2019;ll have the experience of traveling with locals and their produce &#x2013; for example, chickens or vegetables.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/kandy\/ella\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Get Kandy Train Tickets here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Please note<\/strong>: be careful when hanging out the doors or windows of the train as there can be hazards like tree branches on the journey. Make sure to be sat in your seat as the train comes into the station; it can be dangerous to dangle your legs out as the train comes to the platform.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222351\/train-sri-lanka-3.jpg\" alt=\"train kandy ella sri lanka\"><\/noscript><img width=\"236\" height=\"338\" alt=\"train kandy ella sri lanka\" class=\"wp-image-73801 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1343px) 100vw, 1343px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/18222351\/train-sri-lanka-3.jpg 1343w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/w